# Generation 1: greetings & farewells become intent, not echo.
> hello
< Hi there!
> hi
< Hi there!
> hey
< Hi there!
# case-insensitive + surrounding spaces are tolerated
> HELLO
< Hi there!
>   hey
< Hi there!
> bye
< Goodbye!
> goodbye
< Goodbye!
# anything unrecognised still parrots (no regression)
> tell me about C
< tell me about C